{
  "title": "Decadent Croatian Lamb Kebabs",
  "description": "Indulgent Croatian dish featuring lamb, scotch bonnet, and a hint of sweetness, all wrapped in an agave leaf and cooked to perfection in a tandoor, sugar-free-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Croatian",
